<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .header { background: #4F46E5; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 20px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background: #4F46E5; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; }
    .footer { padding: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; text-align: center; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Congratulations! 🎉</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>Your vendor account <strong>{{storeName}}</strong> has been approved.</p>
    <p>You can now:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>List products for sale</li>
      <li>Receive orders from students</li>
      <li>Get paid through our escrow system</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{frontendUrl}}/vendor/dashboard" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>© {{year}} Shopa. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
